import "strings"
import "regexp"
regex = ${RegEX}

fields = ["_time", "GameName", "user", "CarModel", "TrackCode", "SessionId", "SessionTypeName"]
jfields = ["GameName", "user", "CarModel", "TrackCode", "SessionId", "SessionTypeName"]

FinalOutput = ["_field", "_time", "_value"]
StartSession =  time (v: ${SessionStart})
StopSession  = time (v: ${SessionEnd})

data = from(bucket: "racing")
  |> range(start: StartSession, stop: StopSession)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "laps_cc")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["SessionId"] == "${SessionId}")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "CurrentLapTime")
  |> keep(columns: fields)

min = data
  |> first(column: "_time")

max = data
  |> last(column: "_time")

join(tables: {min: min, max: max}, on: jfields, method: "inner")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with SessionId: r.SessionId,
    TrackCode: strings.toLower(v: r.TrackCode),  
    trackShort: regexp.findString(v: r.TrackCode, r: regex)  
    }))
  |> group()  
  
  |> drop(columns: ["SessionId",  "user" ])
  |> yield()
